4576
4577VAStatus DdiMedia_CreateImage(
4578 VADriverContextP ctx,
4579 VAImageFormat *format,
4580 int32_t width,
4581 int32_t height,
4582 VAImage *image /* out */
4583)
4584{
4585 DDI_FUNCTION_ENTER();
4586
4587 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "Invalid context!", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
4588 DDI_CHK_NULL(format, "Invalid format!", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
4589 DDI_CHK_NULL(image, "Invalid image!", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
4590 DDI_CHK_LARGER(width, 0, "Invalid width!", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
4591 DDI_CHK_LARGER(height, 0, "Invalid height!", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
4592 int32_t event[] = {width, height, format->fourcc};
4593 MOS_TraceEventExt(EVENT_VA_IMAGE, EVENT_TYPE_START, event, sizeof(event), nullptr, 0);
4594
4595 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
4596 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx, "nullptr mediaCtx.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
4597 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->pGmmClientContext, "nullptr mediaCtx->pGmmClientContext.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
4598
4599 VAImage *vaimg = (VAImage*)MOS_AllocAndZeroMemory(sizeof(VAImage));
4600 DDI_CHK_NULL(vaimg, "Insufficient to allocate an VAImage.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_ALLOCATION_FAILED);
4601
4602 GMM_RESCREATE_PARAMS gmmParams;
4603 GMM_RESOURCE_INFO *gmmResourceInfo;
4604 MOS_ZeroMemory(&gmmParams, sizeof(gmmParams));
4605
4606 gmmParams.BaseWidth = width;
4607 gmmParams.BaseHeight = height;
4608 gmmParams.ArraySize = 1;
4609 gmmParams.Type = RESOURCE_2D;
4610 gmmParams.Flags.Gpu.Video = true;
4611 gmmParams.Format = mediaCtx->m_caps->ConvertFourccToGmmFmt(format->fourcc);
4612
4613 if (gmmParams.Format == GMM_FORMAT_INVALID)
4614 {
4615 MOS_FreeMemory(vaimg);
4616 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_UNIMPLEMENTED;
4617 }
4618 gmmResourceInfo = mediaCtx->pGmmClientContext->CreateResInfoObject(&gmmParams);
4619 if(nullptr == gmmResourceInfo)
4620 {
4621 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("Gmm Create Resource Failed.");
4622 MOS_FreeMemory(vaimg);
4623 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_ALLOCATION_FAILED;
4624 }
4625
4626 // Get offset from GMM
4627 GMM_REQ_OFFSET_INFO reqInfo = {0};
4628 reqInfo.Plane = GMM_PLANE_U;
4629 reqInfo.ReqRender = 1;
4630 gmmResourceInfo->GetOffset(reqInfo);
4631 uint32_t offsetU = reqInfo.Render.Offset;
4632 MOS_ZeroMemory(&reqInfo, sizeof(GMM_REQ_OFFSET_INFO));
4633 reqInfo.Plane = GMM_PLANE_V;
4634 reqInfo.ReqRender = 1;
4635 gmmResourceInfo->GetOffset(reqInfo);
4636 uint32_t offsetV = reqInfo.Render.Offset;
4637 uint32_t size = (uint32_t)gmmResourceInfo->GetSizeSurface();
4638 uint32_t pitch = (uint32_t)gmmResourceInfo->GetRenderPitch();
4639 vaimg->format = *format;
4640 vaimg->format.byte_order = VA_LSB_FIRST;
4641 vaimg->width = width;
4642 vaimg->height = height;
4643 vaimg->data_size = size;
4644
4645 mediaCtx->pGmmClientContext->DestroyResInfoObject(gmmResourceInfo);
4646
4647 switch(format->fourcc)
4648 {
4649 case VA_FOURCC_RGBA:
4650 case VA_FOURCC_BGRA:
4651 case VA_FOURCC_ARGB:
4652 case VA_FOURCC_ABGR:
4653 case VA_FOURCC_BGRX:
4654 case VA_FOURCC_RGBX:
4655 case VA_FOURCC_XRGB:
4656 case VA_FOURCC_XBGR:
4657 case VA_FOURCC_A2R10G10B10:
4658 case VA_FOURCC_A2B10G10R10:
4659 case VA_FOURCC_X2R10G10B10:
4660 case VA_FOURCC_X2B10G10R10:
4661 case VA_FOURCC_R8G8B8:
4662 case VA_FOURCC_RGB565:
4663 case VA_FOURCC_UYVY:
4664 case VA_FOURCC_YUY2:
4665 case VA_FOURCC_VYUY:
4666 case VA_FOURCC_YVYU:
4667 case VA_FOURCC_AYUV:
4668#if VA_CHECK_VERSION(1, 13, 0)
4669 case VA_FOURCC_XYUV:
4670#endif
4671 case VA_FOURCC_Y210:
4672#if VA_CHECK_VERSION(1, 9, 0)
4673 case VA_FOURCC_Y212:
4674#endif
4675 case VA_FOURCC_Y216:
4676 case VA_FOURCC_Y410:
4677#if VA_CHECK_VERSION(1, 9, 0)
4678 case VA_FOURCC_Y412:
4679#endif
4680 case VA_FOURCC_Y416:
4681 case VA_FOURCC_Y800:
4682 vaimg->num_planes = 1;
4683 vaimg->pitches[0] = pitch;
4684 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4685 break;
4686 case VA_FOURCC_NV12:
4687 case VA_FOURCC_NV21:
4688 case VA_FOURCC_P010:
4689 case VA_FOURCC_P012:
4690 case VA_FOURCC_P016:
4691 vaimg->num_planes = 2;
4692 vaimg->pitches[0] = pitch;
4693 vaimg->pitches[1] = pitch;
4694 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4695 vaimg->offsets[1] = offsetU;
4696 break;
4697 case VA_FOURCC_YV12:
4698 vaimg->num_planes = 3;
4699 vaimg->pitches[0] = pitch;
4700 vaimg->pitches[1] = pitch / 2;
4701 vaimg->pitches[2] = pitch / 2;
4702 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4703 vaimg->offsets[1] = offsetV;
4704 vaimg->offsets[2] = offsetU;
4705 break;
4706 case VA_FOURCC_I420:
4707 vaimg->num_planes = 3;
4708 vaimg->pitches[0] = pitch;
4709 vaimg->pitches[1] = pitch / 2;
4710 vaimg->pitches[2] = pitch / 2;
4711 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4712 vaimg->offsets[1] = offsetU;
4713 vaimg->offsets[2] = offsetV;
4714 break;
4715 case VA_FOURCC_IMC3:
4716 case VA_FOURCC_411P:
4717 case VA_FOURCC_422V:
4718 case VA_FOURCC_422H:
4719 case VA_FOURCC_444P:
4720 case VA_FOURCC_RGBP:
4721 case VA_FOURCC_BGRP:
4722 vaimg->num_planes = 3;
4723 vaimg->pitches[0] = pitch;
4724 vaimg->pitches[1] = pitch;
4725 vaimg->pitches[2] = pitch;
4726 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4727 vaimg->offsets[1] = offsetU;
4728 vaimg->offsets[2] = offsetV;
4729 break;
4730 default:
4731 MOS_FreeMemory(vaimg);
4732 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_UNIMPLEMENTED;
4733 }
4734
4735 DDI_MEDIA_BUFFER *buf = (DDI_MEDIA_BUFFER *)MOS_AllocAndZeroMemory(sizeof(DDI_MEDIA_BUFFER));
4736 if (nullptr == buf)
4737 {
4738 MOS_FreeMemory(vaimg);
4739 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_ALLOCATION_FAILED;
4740 }
4741 buf->uiNumElements = 1;
4742 buf->iSize = vaimg->data_size;
4743 buf->uiType = VAImageBufferType;
4744 buf->format = Media_Format_CPU;//DdiCodec_OsFormatToMediaFormat(vaimg->format.fourcc); //Media_Format_Buffer;
4745 buf->uiOffset = 0;
4746 buf->pMediaCtx = mediaCtx;
4747
4748 //Put Image in untiled buffer for better CPU access?
4749 VAStatus status= DdiMediaUtil_CreateBuffer(buf, mediaCtx->pDrmBufMgr);
4750 if((status != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS))
4751 {
4752 MOS_FreeMemory(vaimg);
4753 MOS_FreeMemory(buf);
4754 return status;
4755 }
4756 buf->TileType = TILING_NONE;
4757
4758 DdiMediaUtil_LockMutex(&mediaCtx->BufferMutex);
4759 PDDI_MEDIA_BUFFER_HEAP_ELEMENT bufferHeapElement = DdiMediaUtil_AllocPMediaBufferFromHeap(mediaCtx->pBufferHeap);
4760
4761 if (nullptr == bufferHeapElement)
4762 {
4763 DdiMediaUtil_UnLockMutex(&mediaCtx->BufferMutex);
4764 MOS_FreeMemory(vaimg);
4765 DdiMediaUtil_FreeBuffer(buf);
4766 MOS_FreeMemory(buf);
4767 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_MAX_NUM_EXCEEDED;
4768 }
4769
4770 bufferHeapElement->pBuffer = buf;
4771 bufferHeapElement->pCtx = nullptr;
4772 bufferHeapElement->uiCtxType = DDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT_TYPE_MEDIA;
4773
4774 vaimg->buf = bufferHeapElement->uiVaBufferID;
4775 mediaCtx->uiNumBufs++;
4776 DdiMediaUtil_UnLockMutex(&mediaCtx->BufferMutex);
4777
4778 DdiMediaUtil_LockMutex(&mediaCtx->ImageMutex);
4779 PDDI_MEDIA_IMAGE_HEAP_ELEMENT imageHeapElement = DdiMediaUtil_AllocPVAImageFromHeap(mediaCtx->pImageHeap);
4780 if (nullptr == imageHeapElement)
4781 {
4782 DdiMediaUtil_UnLockMutex(&mediaCtx->ImageMutex);
4783 MOS_FreeMemory(vaimg);
4784 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_MAX_NUM_EXCEEDED;
4785 }
4786 imageHeapElement->pImage = vaimg;
4787 mediaCtx->uiNumImages++;
4788 vaimg->image_id = imageHeapElement->uiVaImageID;
4789 DdiMediaUtil_UnLockMutex(&mediaCtx->ImageMutex);
4790
4791 *image = *vaimg;
4792 MOS_TraceEventExt(EVENT_VA_IMAGE, EVENT_TYPE_END, &vaimg->image_id, sizeof(VAGenericID), nullptr, 0);
4793 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
4794}
4795
4809VAStatus DdiMedia_DeriveImage (
4810 VADriverContextP ctx,
4811 VASurfaceID surface,
4812 VAImage *image
4813)
4814{
4815 DDI_FUNCTION_ENTER();
4816 MOS_TraceEventExt(EVENT_VA_DERIVE, EVENT_TYPE_START, nullptr, 0, nullptr, 0);
4817
4818 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "nullptr ctx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
4819 DDI_CHK_NULL(image, "nullptr image", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
4820
4821 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
4822 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx, "nullptr mediaCtx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
4823
4824 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap, "nullptr mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
4825 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)surface, mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "Invalid surface", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
4826
4827 DDI_MEDIA_SURFACE *mediaSurface = DdiMedia_GetSurfaceFromVASurfaceID(mediaCtx, surface);
4828 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaSurface, "nullptr mediaSurface", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
4829
4830 VAImage *vaimg = (VAImage*)MOS_AllocAndZeroMemory(sizeof(VAImage));
4831 DDI_CHK_NULL(vaimg, "nullptr vaimg", VA_STATUS_ERROR_ALLOCATION_FAILED);
4832
4833 if (mediaSurface->pCurrentFrameSemaphore)
4834 {
4835 DdiMediaUtil_WaitSemaphore(mediaSurface->pCurrentFrameSemaphore);
4836 DdiMediaUtil_PostSemaphore(mediaSurface->pCurrentFrameSemaphore);
4837 }
4838 DdiMediaUtil_LockMutex(&mediaCtx->ImageMutex);
4839 PDDI_MEDIA_IMAGE_HEAP_ELEMENT imageHeapElement = DdiMediaUtil_AllocPVAImageFromHeap(mediaCtx->pImageHeap);
4840 if (nullptr == imageHeapElement)
4841 {
4842 DdiMediaUtil_UnLockMutex(&mediaCtx->ImageMutex);
4843 MOS_FreeMemory(vaimg);
4844 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_MAX_NUM_EXCEEDED;
4845 }
4846 imageHeapElement->pImage = vaimg;
4847 mediaCtx->uiNumImages++;
4848 vaimg->image_id = imageHeapElement->uiVaImageID;
4849 DdiMediaUtil_UnLockMutex(&mediaCtx->ImageMutex);
4850
4851 vaimg->format.fourcc = DdiMedia_MediaFormatToOsFormat(mediaSurface->format);
4852 vaimg->width = mediaSurface->iWidth;
4853 vaimg->height = mediaSurface->iRealHeight;
4854 vaimg->format.byte_order = VA_LSB_FIRST;
4855
4856 GMM_RESOURCE_INFO *gmmResourceInfo = mediaSurface->pGmmResourceInfo;
4857 GMM_REQ_OFFSET_INFO reqInfo = {0};
4858 reqInfo.Plane = GMM_PLANE_U;
4859 reqInfo.ReqRender = 1;
4860 gmmResourceInfo->GetOffset(reqInfo);
4861 uint32_t offsetU = reqInfo.Render.Offset;
4862 MOS_ZeroMemory(&reqInfo, sizeof(GMM_REQ_OFFSET_INFO));
4863 reqInfo.Plane = GMM_PLANE_V;
4864 reqInfo.ReqRender = 1;
4865 gmmResourceInfo->GetOffset(reqInfo);
4866 uint32_t offsetV = reqInfo.Render.Offset;
4867 vaimg->data_size = (uint32_t)gmmResourceInfo->GetSizeSurface();
4868
4869 switch( mediaSurface->format )
4870 {
4871 case Media_Format_YV12:
4872 case Media_Format_I420:
4873 case Media_Format_IYUV:
4874 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 12;
4875 vaimg->num_planes = 3;
4876 vaimg->pitches[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4877 vaimg->pitches[1] =
4878 vaimg->pitches[2] = mediaSurface->iPitch / 2;
4879 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4880 vaimg->offsets[1] = mediaSurface->iHeight * mediaSurface->iPitch;
4881 vaimg->offsets[2] = vaimg->offsets[1] + vaimg->pitches[1] * MOS_ALIGN_CEIL(mediaSurface->iHeight, 2) / 2;
4882 break;
4883 case Media_Format_A8B8G8R8:
4884 case Media_Format_R8G8B8A8:
4885 case Media_Format_A8R8G8B8:
4886 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 32;
4887 vaimg->format.alpha_mask = RGB_8BIT_ALPHAMASK;
4888 vaimg->num_planes = 1;
4889 vaimg->pitches[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4890 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4891 break;
4892 case Media_Format_X8R8G8B8:
4893 case Media_Format_X8B8G8R8:
4894 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 32;
4895 vaimg->num_planes = 1;
4896 vaimg->pitches[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4897 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4898 break;
4899 case Media_Format_R10G10B10A2:
4900 case Media_Format_B10G10R10A2:
4901 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 32;
4902 vaimg->format.alpha_mask = RGB_10BIT_ALPHAMASK;
4903 vaimg->num_planes = 1;
4904 vaimg->pitches[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4905 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4906 break;
4907 case Media_Format_R10G10B10X2:
4908 case Media_Format_B10G10R10X2:
4909 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 32;
4910 vaimg->num_planes = 1;
4911 vaimg->pitches[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4912 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4913 break;
4914 case Media_Format_R5G6B5:
4915 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 16;
4916 vaimg->data_size = mediaSurface->iPitch * mediaSurface->iHeight;
4917 vaimg->num_planes = 1;
4918 vaimg->pitches[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4919 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4920 break;
4921 case Media_Format_R8G8B8:
4922 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 24;
4923 vaimg->num_planes = 1;
4924 vaimg->pitches[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4925 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4926 break;
4927 case Media_Format_YUY2:
4928 case Media_Format_UYVY:
4929 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 16;
4930 vaimg->data_size = mediaSurface->iPitch * mediaSurface->iHeight;
4931 vaimg->num_planes = 1;
4932 vaimg->pitches[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4933 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4934 break;
4935 case Media_Format_400P:
4936 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 8;
4937 vaimg->num_planes = 1;
4938 vaimg->pitches[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4939 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4940 break;
4941 case Media_Format_444P:
4942 case Media_Format_RGBP:
4943 case Media_Format_BGRP:
4944 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 24;
4945 vaimg->num_planes = 3;
4946 vaimg->pitches[0] =
4947 vaimg->pitches[1] =
4948 vaimg->pitches[2] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4949 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4950 vaimg->offsets[1] = mediaSurface->iHeight * mediaSurface->iPitch;
4951 vaimg->offsets[2] = mediaSurface->iHeight * mediaSurface->iPitch * 2;
4952 break;
4953 case Media_Format_IMC3:
4954 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 12;
4955 vaimg->num_planes = 3;
4956 vaimg->pitches[0] =
4957 vaimg->pitches[1] =
4958 vaimg->pitches[2] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4959 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4960 vaimg->offsets[1] = mediaSurface->iHeight * mediaSurface->iPitch;
4961 vaimg->offsets[2] = mediaSurface->iHeight * mediaSurface->iPitch * 3 / 2;
4962 break;
4963 case Media_Format_411P:
4964 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 12;
4965 vaimg->num_planes = 3;
4966 vaimg->pitches[0] =
4967 vaimg->pitches[1] =
4968 vaimg->pitches[2] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4969 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4970 vaimg->offsets[1] = mediaSurface->iHeight * mediaSurface->iPitch;
4971 vaimg->offsets[2] = mediaSurface->iHeight * mediaSurface->iPitch * 2;
4972 break;
4973 case Media_Format_422V:
4974 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 16;
4975 vaimg->num_planes = 3;
4976 vaimg->pitches[0] =
4977 vaimg->pitches[1] =
4978 vaimg->pitches[2] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4979 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4980 vaimg->offsets[1] = mediaSurface->iHeight * mediaSurface->iPitch;
4981 vaimg->offsets[2] = mediaSurface->iHeight * mediaSurface->iPitch * 3 / 2;
4982 break;
4983 case Media_Format_422H:
4984 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 16;
4985 vaimg->num_planes = 3;
4986 vaimg->pitches[0] =
4987 vaimg->pitches[1] =
4988 vaimg->pitches[2] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4989 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
4990 vaimg->offsets[1] = mediaSurface->iHeight * mediaSurface->iPitch;
4991 vaimg->offsets[2] = mediaSurface->iHeight * mediaSurface->iPitch * 2;
4992 break;
4993 case Media_Format_P010:
4994 case Media_Format_P012:
4995 case Media_Format_P016:
4996 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 24;
4997 vaimg->num_planes = 2;
4998 vaimg->pitches[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
4999 vaimg->pitches[1] =
5000 vaimg->pitches[2] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
5001 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
5002 vaimg->offsets[1] = mediaSurface->iHeight * mediaSurface->iPitch;
5003 vaimg->offsets[2] = vaimg->offsets[1] + 2;
5004 break;
5005 case Media_Format_Y410:
5006 case Media_Format_AYUV:
5007#if VA_CHECK_VERSION(1, 13, 0)
5008 case Media_Format_XYUV:
5009#endif
5010 case Media_Format_Y210:
5011#if VA_CHECK_VERSION(1, 9, 0)
5012 case Media_Format_Y212:
5013#endif
5014 case Media_Format_Y216:
5015 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 32;
5016 vaimg->data_size = mediaSurface->iPitch * mediaSurface->iHeight;
5017 vaimg->num_planes = 1;
5018 vaimg->pitches[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
5019 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
5020 break;
5021#if VA_CHECK_VERSION(1, 9, 0)
5022 case Media_Format_Y412:
5023#endif
5024 case Media_Format_Y416:
5025 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 64; // packed format [alpha, Y, U, V], 16 bits per channel
5026 vaimg->num_planes = 1;
5027 vaimg->pitches[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
5028 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
5029 break;
5030 default:
5031 vaimg->format.bits_per_pixel = 12;
5032 vaimg->num_planes = 2;
5033 vaimg->pitches[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
5034 vaimg->pitches[1] =
5035 vaimg->pitches[2] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
5036 vaimg->offsets[0] = 0;
5037 if(MEDIA_IS_WA(&mediaCtx->WaTable, WaDisableGmmLibOffsetInDeriveImage))
5038 {
5039 vaimg->offsets[1] = mediaSurface->iHeight * mediaSurface->iPitch;
5040 vaimg->offsets[2] = vaimg->offsets[1] + 1;
5041 }
5042 else
5043 {
5044 vaimg->offsets[1] = offsetU;
5045 vaimg->offsets[2] = offsetV;
5046 }
5047 break;
5048 }
5049
5050 if ((mediaSurface->pSurfDesc != nullptr) && (mediaSurface->pSurfDesc->uiVaMemType == VA_SURFACE_ATTRIB_MEM_TYPE_USER_PTR))
5051 {
5052 vaimg->num_planes = mediaSurface->pSurfDesc->uiPlanes;
5053 for (uint32_t i = 0; i < vaimg->num_planes; i++)
5054 {
5055 vaimg->pitches[i] = mediaSurface->pSurfDesc->uiPitches[i];
5056 vaimg->offsets[i] = mediaSurface->pSurfDesc->uiOffsets[i];
5057 }
5058 }
5059
5060 mediaCtx->m_caps->PopulateColorMaskInfo(&vaimg->format);
5061
5062 DDI_MEDIA_BUFFER *buf = (DDI_MEDIA_BUFFER *)MOS_AllocAndZeroMemory(sizeof(DDI_MEDIA_BUFFER));
5063 if (buf == nullptr)
5064 {
5065 MOS_FreeMemory(vaimg);
5066 MOS_FreeMemory(buf);
5067 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_ALLOCATION_FAILED;
5068 }
5069 buf->uiNumElements = 1;
5070 buf->iSize = vaimg->data_size;
5071 buf->uiType = VAImageBufferType;
5072 buf->format = mediaSurface->format;
5073 buf->uiOffset = 0;
5074
5075 buf->bo = mediaSurface->bo;
5076 buf->format = mediaSurface->format;
5077 buf->TileType = mediaSurface->TileType;
5078 buf->pSurface = mediaSurface;
5079 mos_bo_reference(mediaSurface->bo);
5080
5081 DdiMediaUtil_LockMutex(&mediaCtx->BufferMutex);
5082 PDDI_MEDIA_BUFFER_HEAP_ELEMENT bufferHeapElement = DdiMediaUtil_AllocPMediaBufferFromHeap(mediaCtx->pBufferHeap);
5083
5084 if (nullptr == bufferHeapElement)
5085 {
5086 DdiMediaUtil_UnLockMutex(&mediaCtx->BufferMutex);
5087 MOS_FreeMemory(vaimg);
5088 MOS_FreeMemory(buf);
5089 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_MAX_NUM_EXCEEDED;
5090 }
5091 bufferHeapElement->pBuffer = buf;
5092 bufferHeapElement->pCtx = nullptr;
5093 bufferHeapElement->uiCtxType = DDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT_TYPE_MEDIA;
5094
5095 vaimg->buf = bufferHeapElement->uiVaBufferID;
5096 mediaCtx->uiNumBufs++;
5097 DdiMediaUtil_UnLockMutex(&mediaCtx->BufferMutex);
5098
5099 *image = *vaimg;
5100
5101 MOS_TraceEventExt(EVENT_VA_DERIVE, EVENT_TYPE_END, &surface, sizeof(surface), &vaimg->image_id, sizeof(VAGenericID));
5102 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
5103}

5116VAStatus DdiMedia_DestroyImage (
5117 VADriverContextP ctx,
5118 VAImageID image)
5119{
5120 DDI_FUNCTION_ENTER();
5121 MOS_TraceEventExt(EVENT_VA_FREE_IMAGE, EVENT_TYPE_START, &image, sizeof(image), nullptr, 0);
5122
5123 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "nullptr ctx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
5124 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
5125
5126 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx, "nullptr Media", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
5127 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->pImageHeap, "nullptr mediaCtx->pImageHeap", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
5128 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)image, mediaCtx->pImageHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "Invalid image", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_IMAGE);
5129
5130 VAImage *vaImage = DdiMedia_GetVAImageFromVAImageID(mediaCtx, image);
5131 if (vaImage == nullptr)
5132 {
5133 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER;
5134 }
5135 DdiMedia_DestroyBuffer(ctx, vaImage->buf);
5136 MOS_FreeMemory(vaImage);
5137
5138 DdiMedia_DestroyImageFromVAImageID(mediaCtx, image);
5139
5140 MOS_TraceEventExt(EVENT_VA_FREE_IMAGE, EVENT_TYPE_END, nullptr, 0, nullptr, 0);
5141 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
5142}

5170
5171VAStatus SwizzleSurface(PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx, PGMM_RESOURCE_INFO pGmmResInfo, void *pLockedAddr, uint32_t TileType, uint8_t* pResourceBase, bool bUpload)
5172{
5173 uint32_t uiSize, uiPitch;
5174 GMM_RES_COPY_BLT gmmResCopyBlt;
5175 uint32_t uiPicHeight;
5176 uint32_t ulSwizzledSize;
5177 VAStatus vaStatus = VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
5178
5179 DDI_CHK_NULL(pGmmResInfo, "pGmmResInfo is NULL", VA_STATUS_ERROR_OPERATION_FAILED);
5180 DDI_CHK_NULL(pLockedAddr, "pLockedAddr is NULL", VA_STATUS_ERROR_OPERATION_FAILED);
5181 DDI_CHK_NULL(pResourceBase, "pResourceBase is NULL", VA_STATUS_ERROR_ALLOCATION_FAILED);
5182
5183 memset(&gmmResCopyBlt, 0x0, sizeof(GMM_RES_COPY_BLT));
5184 uiPicHeight = pGmmResInfo->GetBaseHeight();
5185 uiSize = pGmmResInfo->GetSizeMainSurface();
5186 uiPitch = pGmmResInfo->GetRenderPitch();
5187 gmmResCopyBlt.Gpu.pData = pLockedAddr;
5188 gmmResCopyBlt.Sys.pData = pResourceBase;
5189 gmmResCopyBlt.Sys.RowPitch = uiPitch;
5190 gmmResCopyBlt.Sys.BufferSize = uiSize;
5191 gmmResCopyBlt.Sys.SlicePitch = uiSize;
5192 gmmResCopyBlt.Blt.Slices = 1;
5193 gmmResCopyBlt.Blt.Upload = bUpload;
5194
5195 if(mediaCtx->pGmmClientContext->IsPlanar(pGmmResInfo->GetResourceFormat()) == true)
5196 {
5197 gmmResCopyBlt.Blt.Width = pGmmResInfo->GetBaseWidth();
5198 gmmResCopyBlt.Blt.Height = uiSize/uiPitch;
5199 }
5200
5201 pGmmResInfo->CpuBlt(&gmmResCopyBlt);
5202
5203 return vaStatus;
5204}
5205
5220static void DdiMedia_CopyPlane(
5221 uint8_t *dst,
5222 uint32_t dstPitch,
5223 uint8_t *src,
5224 uint32_t srcPitch,
5225 uint32_t height)
5226{
5227 uint32_t rowSize = std::min(dstPitch, srcPitch);
5228 for (int y = 0; y < height; y += 1)
5229 {
5230 memcpy(dst, src, rowSize);
5231 dst += dstPitch;
5232 src += srcPitch;
5233 }
5234}
5235
5249static VAStatus DdiMedia_CopySurfaceToImage(
5250 VADriverContextP ctx,
5251 DDI_MEDIA_SURFACE *surface,
5252 VAImage *image)
5253{
5254 DDI_FUNCTION_ENTER();
5255
5256 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "nullptr ctx.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
5257 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
5258 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx, "nullptr mediaCtx.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
5259 DDI_CHK_NULL(surface, "nullptr meida surface.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER);
5260 uint32_t flag = MOS_LOCKFLAG_READONLY;
5261 VAStatus vaStatus = VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
5262
5263 //Lock Surface
5264 if ((Media_Format_CPU != surface->format))
5265 {
5266 vaStatus = DdiMedia_MediaMemoryDecompress(mediaCtx, surface);
5267
5268 if (vaStatus != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS)
5269 {
5270 DDI_NORMALMESSAGE("surface Decompression fail, continue next steps.");
5271 }
5272 }
5273
5274 void* surfData = DdiMediaUtil_LockSurface(surface, flag);
5275
5276 if (surfData == nullptr)
5277 {
5278 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("nullptr surfData.");
5279 return vaStatus;
5280 }
5281
5282 void *imageData = nullptr;
5283 vaStatus = DdiMedia_MapBuffer(ctx, image->buf, &imageData);
5284 if (vaStatus != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS)
5285 {
5286 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("Failed to map buffer.");
5287 DdiMediaUtil_UnlockSurface(surface);
5288 return vaStatus;
5289 }
5290
5291 uint8_t *ySrc = (uint8_t*)surfData;
5292 uint8_t *yDst = (uint8_t*)imageData;
5293
5294 DdiMedia_CopyPlane(yDst, image->pitches[0], ySrc, surface->iPitch, image->height);
5295 if (image->num_planes > 1)
5296 {
5297 uint8_t *uSrc = ySrc + surface->iPitch * surface->iHeight;
5298 uint8_t *uDst = yDst + image->offsets[1];
5299 uint32_t chromaPitch = 0;
5300 uint32_t chromaHeight = 0;
5301 uint32_t imageChromaPitch = 0;
5302 uint32_t imageChromaHeight = 0;
5303 DdiMedia_GetChromaPitchHeight(DdiMedia_MediaFormatToOsFormat(surface->format), surface->iPitch, surface->iHeight, &chromaPitch, &chromaHeight);
5304 DdiMedia_GetChromaPitchHeight(image->format.fourcc, image->pitches[0], image->height, &imageChromaPitch, &imageChromaHeight);
5305 DdiMedia_CopyPlane(uDst, image->pitches[1], uSrc, chromaPitch, imageChromaHeight);
5306
5307 if(image->num_planes > 2)
5308 {
5309 uint8_t *vSrc = uSrc + chromaPitch * chromaHeight;
5310 uint8_t *vDst = yDst + image->offsets[2];
5311 DdiMedia_CopyPlane(vDst, image->pitches[2], vSrc, chromaPitch, imageChromaHeight);
5312 }
5313 }
5314
5315 vaStatus = DdiMedia_UnmapBuffer(ctx, image->buf);
5316 if (vaStatus != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS)
5317 {
5318 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("Failed to unmap buffer.");
5319 DdiMediaUtil_UnlockSurface(surface);
5320 return vaStatus;
5321 }
5322
5323 DdiMediaUtil_UnlockSurface(surface);
5324
5325 return vaStatus;
5326}
5327
5350VAStatus DdiMedia_GetImage(
5351 VADriverContextP ctx,
5352 VASurfaceID surface,
5353 int32_t x, /* coordinates of the upper left source pixel */
5354 int32_t y,
5355 uint32_t width, /* width and height of the region */
5356 uint32_t height,
5357 VAImageID image
5358)
5359{
5360 DDI_FUNCTION_ENTER();
5361 uint32_t event[] = {surface, x, y, width, height, image};
5362 MOS_TraceEventExt(EVENT_VA_GET, EVENT_TYPE_START, &event, sizeof(event), nullptr, 0);
5363
5364 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "nullptr ctx.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
5365
5366 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
5367 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx, "nullptr mediaCtx.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
5368
5369 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap, "nullptr mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
5370 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->pImageHeap, "nullptr mediaCtx->pImageHeap.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
5371 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)surface, mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "Invalid surface.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
5372 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)image, mediaCtx->pImageHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "Invalid image.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_IMAGE);
5373
5374 VAImage *vaimg = DdiMedia_GetVAImageFromVAImageID(mediaCtx, image);
5375 DDI_CHK_NULL(vaimg, "nullptr vaimg.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_IMAGE);
5376
5377 DDI_MEDIA_BUFFER *buf = DdiMedia_GetBufferFromVABufferID(mediaCtx, vaimg->buf);
5378 DDI_CHK_NULL(buf, "nullptr buf.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER);
5379
5380 DDI_MEDIA_SURFACE *inputSurface = DdiMedia_GetSurfaceFromVASurfaceID(mediaCtx, surface);
5381 DDI_CHK_NULL(inputSurface, "nullptr inputSurface.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
5382 DDI_CHK_NULL(inputSurface->bo, "nullptr inputSurface->bo.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
5383
5384 VAStatus vaStatus = VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
5385#ifndef _FULL_OPEN_SOURCE
5386 VASurfaceID target_surface = VA_INVALID_SURFACE;
5387 VASurfaceID output_surface = surface;
5388
5389 if (inputSurface->format != DdiMedia_OsFormatToMediaFormat(vaimg->format.fourcc, vaimg->format.alpha_mask) ||
5390 (width != vaimg->width || height != vaimg->height) &&
5391 (vaimg->format.fourcc != VA_FOURCC_444P &&
5392 vaimg->format.fourcc != VA_FOURCC_422V &&
5393 vaimg->format.fourcc != VA_FOURCC_422H))
5394 {
5395 VAContextID context = VA_INVALID_ID;
5396 //Create VP Context.
5397 vaStatus = DdiVp_CreateContext(ctx, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, &context);
5398 DDI_CHK_RET(vaStatus, "Create VP Context failed.");
5399
5400 //Create target surface for VP pipeline.
5401 DDI_MEDIA_FORMAT mediaFmt = DdiMedia_OsFormatToMediaFormat(vaimg->format.fourcc, vaimg->format.fourcc);
5402 if (mediaFmt == Media_Format_Count)
5403 {
5404 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("Unsupported surface type.");
5405 DdiVp_DestroyContext(ctx, context);
5406 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_UNSUPPORTED_RT_FORMAT;
5407 }
5408 PDDI_MEDIA_SURFACE_DESCRIPTOR surfDesc = (PDDI_MEDIA_SURFACE_DESCRIPTOR)MOS_AllocAndZeroMemory(sizeof(DDI_MEDIA_SURFACE_DESCRIPTOR));
5409 if (!surfDesc) {
5410 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("nullptr surfDesc.");
5411 DdiVp_DestroyContext(ctx, context);
5412 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_ALLOCATION_FAILED;
5413 }
5414 surfDesc->uiVaMemType = VA_SURFACE_ATTRIB_MEM_TYPE_VA;
5415 int memType = MOS_MEMPOOL_VIDEOMEMORY;
5416 if (MEDIA_IS_SKU(&mediaCtx->SkuTable, FtrLocalMemory))
5417 {
5418 memType = MOS_MEMPOOL_SYSTEMMEMORY;
5419 }
5420 target_surface = (VASurfaceID)DdiMedia_CreateRenderTarget(mediaCtx, mediaFmt, vaimg->width, vaimg->height, surfDesc, VA_SURFACE_ATTRIB_USAGE_HINT_GENERIC, memType);
5421 if (VA_INVALID_SURFACE == target_surface)
5422 {
5423 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("Create temp surface failed.");
5424 DdiVp_DestroyContext(ctx, context);
5425 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_ALLOCATION_FAILED;
5426 }
5427
5428 VARectangle srcRect, dstRect;
5429 srcRect.x = x;
5430 srcRect.y = y;
5431 srcRect.width = width;
5432 srcRect.height = height;
5433 dstRect.x = 0;
5434 dstRect.y = 0;
5435 dstRect.width = vaimg->width;
5436 dstRect.height = vaimg->height;
5437
5438 //Execute VP pipeline.
5439 vaStatus = DdiVp_VideoProcessPipeline(ctx, context, surface, &srcRect, target_surface, &dstRect);
5440 if (vaStatus != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS)
5441 {
5442 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("VP Pipeline failed.");
5443 DdiMedia_DestroySurfaces(ctx, &target_surface, 1);
5444 DdiVp_DestroyContext(ctx, context);
5445 return vaStatus;
5446 }
5447 vaStatus = DdiMedia_SyncSurface(ctx, target_surface);
5448 if (vaStatus != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS)
5449 {
5450 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("VP Sync surface failed.");
5451 }
5452 vaStatus = DdiVp_DestroyContext(ctx, context);
5453 if (vaStatus != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS)
5454 {
5455 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("VP Destroy Context failed.");
5456 }
5457 output_surface = target_surface;
5458 }
5459
5460 //Get Media Surface from output surface ID
5461 DDI_MEDIA_SURFACE *mediaSurface = DdiMedia_GetSurfaceFromVASurfaceID(mediaCtx, output_surface);
5462 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaSurface, "nullptr mediaSurface.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
5463 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaSurface->bo, "nullptr mediaSurface->bo.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
5464
5465 vaStatus = DdiMedia_CopySurfaceToImage(ctx, mediaSurface, vaimg);
5466
5467 if (vaStatus != MOS_STATUS_SUCCESS)
5468 {
5469 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("Failed to copy surface to image buffer data!");
5470 if(target_surface != VA_INVALID_SURFACE)
5471 {
5472 DdiMedia_DestroySurfaces(ctx, &target_surface, 1);
5473 }
5474 return vaStatus;
5475 }
5476
5477 //Destroy temp surface if created
5478 if(target_surface != VA_INVALID_SURFACE)
5479 {
5480 DdiMedia_DestroySurfaces(ctx, &target_surface, 1);
5481 }
5482#else
5483 vaStatus = DdiMedia_CopySurfaceToImage(ctx, inputSurface, vaimg);
5484 DDI_CHK_RET(vaStatus, "Copy surface to image failed.");
5485#endif
5486 MOS_TraceEventExt(EVENT_VA_GET, EVENT_TYPE_END, nullptr, 0, nullptr, 0);
5487 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
5488}
5489
5520VAStatus DdiMedia_PutImage(
5521 VADriverContextP ctx,
5522 VASurfaceID surface,
5523 VAImageID image,
5524 int32_t src_x,
5525 int32_t src_y,
5526 uint32_t src_width,
5527 uint32_t src_height,
5528 int32_t dest_x,
5529 int32_t dest_y,
5530 uint32_t dest_width,
5531 uint32_t dest_height
5532)
5533{
5534 DDI_FUNCTION_ENTER();
5535 uint32_t event[] = {surface, image, src_x, src_y, src_width, src_height, dest_x, dest_y, dest_width, dest_height};
5536 MOS_TraceEventExt(EVENT_VA_PUT, EVENT_TYPE_START, &event, sizeof(event), nullptr, 0);
5537
5538 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "nullptr ctx.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
5539
5540 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
5541 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx, "nullptr mediaCtx.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
5542
5543 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap, "nullptr mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
5544 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->pImageHeap, "nullptr mediaCtx->pImageHeap.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
5545 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)surface, mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "Invalid surface.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
5546 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)image, mediaCtx->pImageHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "Invalid image.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_IMAGE);
5547
5548 DDI_MEDIA_SURFACE *mediaSurface = DdiMedia_GetSurfaceFromVASurfaceID(mediaCtx, surface);
5549 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaSurface, "nullptr mediaSurface.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
5550 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaSurface->bo, "Invalid buffer.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER);
5551
5552 if (mediaSurface->pCurrentFrameSemaphore)
5553 {
5554 DdiMediaUtil_WaitSemaphore(mediaSurface->pCurrentFrameSemaphore);
5555 DdiMediaUtil_PostSemaphore(mediaSurface->pCurrentFrameSemaphore);
5556 }
5557
5558 VAImage *vaimg = DdiMedia_GetVAImageFromVAImageID(mediaCtx, image);
5559 DDI_CHK_NULL(vaimg, "Invalid image.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_IMAGE);
5560
5561 DDI_MEDIA_BUFFER *buf = DdiMedia_GetBufferFromVABufferID(mediaCtx, vaimg->buf);
5562 DDI_CHK_NULL(buf, "Invalid buffer.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER);
5563
5564 VAStatus vaStatus = VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
5565 void *imageData = nullptr;
5566
5567 vaStatus = DdiMedia_MapBuffer(ctx, vaimg->buf, &imageData);
5568 DDI_CHK_RET(vaStatus, "MapBuffer failed.");
5569 DDI_CHK_NULL(imageData, "nullptr imageData.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_IMAGE);
5570
5571 // VP Pipeline will be called for CSC/Scaling if the surface format or data size is not consistent with image.
5572 if (mediaSurface->format != DdiMedia_OsFormatToMediaFormat(vaimg->format.fourcc, vaimg->format.alpha_mask) ||
5573 dest_width != src_width || dest_height != src_height ||
5574 src_x != 0 || dest_x != 0 || src_y != 0 || dest_y != 0)
5575 {
5576 VAContextID context = VA_INVALID_ID;
5577
5578 //Create VP Context.
5579 vaStatus = DdiVp_CreateContext(ctx, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, &context);
5580 DDI_CHK_RET(vaStatus, "Create VP Context failed");
5581
5582 //Create temp surface for VP pipeline.
5583 DDI_MEDIA_FORMAT mediaFmt = DdiMedia_OsFormatToMediaFormat(vaimg->format.fourcc, vaimg->format.fourcc);
5584 if (mediaFmt == Media_Format_Count)
5585 {
5586 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("Unsupported surface type.");
5587 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_UNSUPPORTED_RT_FORMAT;
5588 }
5589
5590 int memType = MOS_MEMPOOL_VIDEOMEMORY;
5591 if (MEDIA_IS_SKU(&mediaCtx->SkuTable, FtrLocalMemory))
5592 {
5593 memType = MOS_MEMPOOL_SYSTEMMEMORY;
5594 }
5595 VASurfaceID tempSurface = (VASurfaceID)DdiMedia_CreateRenderTarget(mediaCtx, mediaFmt, vaimg->width, vaimg->height, nullptr, VA_SURFACE_ATTRIB_USAGE_HINT_VPP_READ, memType);
5596 if (tempSurface == VA_INVALID_ID)
5597 {
5598 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_ALLOCATION_FAILED;
5599 }
5600
5601 DDI_MEDIA_SURFACE *tempMediaSurface = DdiMedia_GetSurfaceFromVASurfaceID(mediaCtx, tempSurface);
5602 DDI_CHK_NULL(tempMediaSurface, "nullptr tempMediaSurface.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
5603
5604 //Lock Surface
5605 void *tempSurfData = DdiMediaUtil_LockSurface(tempMediaSurface, (MOS_LOCKFLAG_READONLY | MOS_LOCKFLAG_WRITEONLY));
5606 if (nullptr == tempSurfData)
5607 {
5608 DdiMedia_DestroySurfaces(ctx, &tempSurface, 1);
5609 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_SURFACE_BUSY;
5610 }
5611
5612 //Copy data from image to temp surferce
5613 MOS_STATUS eStatus = MOS_SecureMemcpy(tempSurfData, vaimg->data_size, imageData, vaimg->data_size);
5614 if (eStatus != MOS_STATUS_SUCCESS)
5615 {
5616 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("Failed to copy image to surface buffer.");
5617 DdiMediaUtil_UnlockSurface(tempMediaSurface);
5618 DdiMedia_DestroySurfaces(ctx, &tempSurface, 1);
5619 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_OPERATION_FAILED;
5620 }
5621
5622 vaStatus = DdiMedia_UnmapBuffer(ctx, vaimg->buf);
5623 if (vaStatus != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS)
5624 {
5625 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("Failed to unmap buffer.");
5626 DdiMediaUtil_UnlockSurface(tempMediaSurface);
5627 DdiMedia_DestroySurfaces(ctx, &tempSurface, 1);
5628 return vaStatus;
5629 }
5630
5631 DdiMediaUtil_UnlockSurface(tempMediaSurface);
5632
5633 VARectangle srcRect, dstRect;
5634 srcRect.x = src_x;
5635 srcRect.y = src_y;
5636 srcRect.width = src_width;
5637 srcRect.height = src_height;
5638 dstRect.x = dest_x;
5639 dstRect.y = dest_y;
5640 dstRect.width = dest_width;
5641 dstRect.height = dest_height;
5642
5643 //Execute VP pipeline.
5644 vaStatus = DdiVp_VideoProcessPipeline(ctx, context, tempSurface, &srcRect, surface, &dstRect);
5645 if (vaStatus != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS)
5646 {
5647 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("VP Pipeline failed.");
5648 DdiMedia_DestroySurfaces(ctx, &tempSurface, 1);
5649 return vaStatus;
5650 }
5651
5652 vaStatus = DdiMedia_SyncSurface(ctx, tempSurface);
5653 DdiMedia_DestroySurfaces(ctx, &tempSurface, 1);
5654 vaStatus = DdiVp_DestroyContext(ctx, context);
5655 }
5656 else
5657 {
5658 //Lock Surface
5659 if ((nullptr != buf->pSurface) && (Media_Format_CPU != mediaSurface->format))
5660 {
5661 vaStatus = DdiMedia_MediaMemoryDecompress(mediaCtx, mediaSurface);
5662
5663 if (vaStatus != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS)
5664 {
5665 DDI_NORMALMESSAGE("surface Decompression fail, continue next steps.");
5666 }
5667 }
5668
5669 void *surfData = DdiMediaUtil_LockSurface(mediaSurface, (MOS_LOCKFLAG_READONLY | MOS_LOCKFLAG_WRITEONLY));
5670 if (nullptr == surfData)
5671 {
5672 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("Failed to lock surface.");
5673 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_SURFACE_BUSY;
5674 }
5675
5676 if (src_width == dest_width && src_height == dest_height &&
5677 src_width == vaimg->width && src_height == vaimg->height &&
5678 src_width == mediaSurface->iWidth && src_height == mediaSurface->iHeight &&
5679 mediaSurface->data_size == vaimg->data_size)
5680 {
5681 //Copy data from image to surface
5682 MOS_STATUS eStatus = MOS_SecureMemcpy(surfData, vaimg->data_size, imageData, vaimg->data_size);
5683 DDI_CHK_CONDITION((eStatus != MOS_STATUS_SUCCESS), "Failed to copy image to surface buffer.", VA_STATUS_ERROR_OPERATION_FAILED);
5684 }
5685 else
5686 {
5687 uint8_t *ySrc = (uint8_t *)imageData + vaimg->offsets[0];
5688 uint8_t *yDst = (uint8_t *)surfData;
5689 DdiMedia_CopyPlane(yDst, mediaSurface->iPitch, ySrc, vaimg->pitches[0], src_height);
5690
5691 if (vaimg->num_planes > 1)
5692 {
5693 DDI_MEDIA_SURFACE uPlane = *mediaSurface;
5694
5695 uint32_t chromaHeight = 0;
5696 uint32_t chromaPitch = 0;
5697 DdiMedia_GetChromaPitchHeight(DdiMedia_MediaFormatToOsFormat(uPlane.format), uPlane.iPitch, uPlane.iHeight, &chromaPitch, &chromaHeight);
5698
5699 uint8_t *uSrc = (uint8_t *)imageData + vaimg->offsets[1];
5700 uint8_t *uDst = yDst + mediaSurface->iPitch * mediaSurface->iHeight;
5701 DdiMedia_CopyPlane(uDst, chromaPitch, uSrc, vaimg->pitches[1], chromaHeight);
5702 if (vaimg->num_planes > 2)
5703 {
5704 uint8_t *vSrc = (uint8_t *)imageData + vaimg->offsets[2];
5705 uint8_t *vDst = uDst + chromaPitch * chromaHeight;
5706 DdiMedia_CopyPlane(vDst, chromaPitch, vSrc, vaimg->pitches[2], chromaHeight);
5707 }
5708 }
5709 }
5710
5711 vaStatus = DdiMedia_UnmapBuffer(ctx, vaimg->buf);
5712 if (vaStatus != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS)
5713 {
5714 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("Failed to unmap buffer.");
5715 DdiMediaUtil_UnlockSurface(mediaSurface);
5716 return vaStatus;
5717 }
5718
5719 DdiMediaUtil_UnlockSurface(mediaSurface);
5720 }
5721 MOS_TraceEventExt(EVENT_VA_PUT, EVENT_TYPE_END, nullptr, 0, nullptr, 0);
5722 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
5723}

6051VAStatus DdiMedia_GetDisplayAttributes(

6146VAStatus
6147DdiMedia_CopyInternal(
6148 PMOS_CONTEXT mosCtx,
6149 PMOS_RESOURCE src,
6150 PMOS_RESOURCE dst,
6151 uint32_t copy_mode
6152)
6153{
6154 VAStatus vaStatus = VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
6155 MOS_STATUS mosStatus = MOS_STATUS_UNINITIALIZED;
6156 DDI_CHK_NULL(mosCtx, "nullptr mosCtx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6157 DDI_CHK_NULL(src, "nullptr input osResource", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
6158 DDI_CHK_NULL(dst, "nullptr output osResource", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
6159
6160 MediaCopyBaseState *mediaCopyState = static_cast<MediaCopyBaseState*>(*mosCtx->ppMediaCopyState);
6161
6162 if (!mediaCopyState)
6163 {
6164 mediaCopyState = static_cast<MediaCopyBaseState*>(McpyDevice::CreateFactory(mosCtx));
6165 *mosCtx->ppMediaCopyState = mediaCopyState;
6166 }
6167
6168 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCopyState, "Invalid mediaCopy State", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6169
6170 mosStatus = mediaCopyState->SurfaceCopy(src, dst, (MCPY_METHOD)copy_mode);
6171 if (mosStatus != MOS_STATUS_SUCCESS)
6172 {
6173 vaStatus = VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER;
6174 }
6175
6176 return vaStatus;
6177}
6178
6179#if VA_CHECK_VERSION(1,10,0)
6197VAStatus
6198DdiMedia_Copy(
6199 VADriverContextP ctx,
6200 VACopyObject *dst_obj,
6201 VACopyObject *src_obj,
6202 VACopyOption option
6203)
6204{
6205 VAStatus vaStatus = VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
6206 MOS_CONTEXT mosCtx = {};
6207 MOS_RESOURCE src, dst;
6208 DdiCpInterface *pCpDdiInterface = nullptr;
6209 PDDI_MEDIA_SURFACE src_surface = nullptr;
6210 PDDI_MEDIA_SURFACE dst_surface = nullptr;
6211 PDDI_MEDIA_BUFFER src_buffer = nullptr;
6212 PDDI_MEDIA_BUFFER dst_buffer = nullptr;
6213
6214 DDI_FUNCTION_ENTER();
6215
6216 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "nullptr ctx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6217 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
6218
6219 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx, "nullptr mediaCtx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6220 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->pBufferHeap, "nullptr mediaCtx->pBufferHeap", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6221 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap, "nullptr mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6222 DDI_CHK_NULL(dst_obj, "nullptr copy dst", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
6223 DDI_CHK_NULL(src_obj, "nullptr copy src", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
6224
6225 if (dst_obj->obj_type == VACopyObjectSurface)
6226 {
6227 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)dst_obj->object.surface_id, mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "copy_dst", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
6228 dst_surface = DdiMedia_GetSurfaceFromVASurfaceID(mediaCtx, dst_obj->object.surface_id);
6229 DDI_CHK_NULL(dst_surface, "nullptr surface", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
6230 DDI_CHK_NULL(dst_surface->pGmmResourceInfo, "nullptr dst_surface->pGmmResourceInfo", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6231
6232 MOS_ZeroMemory(&dst, sizeof(dst));
6233 DdiMedia_MediaSurfaceToMosResource(dst_surface, &dst);
6234 }
6235 else if (dst_obj->obj_type == VACopyObjectBuffer)
6236 {
6237 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)dst_obj->object.buffer_id, mediaCtx->pBufferHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "Invalid copy dst buf_id", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER);
6238 dst_buffer = DdiMedia_GetBufferFromVABufferID(mediaCtx, dst_obj->object.buffer_id);
6239 DDI_CHK_NULL(dst_buffer, "nullptr buffer", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER);
6240 DDI_CHK_NULL(dst_buffer->pGmmResourceInfo, "nullptr dst_buffer->pGmmResourceInfo", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6241
6242 MOS_ZeroMemory(&dst, sizeof(dst));
6243 DdiMedia_MediaBufferToMosResource(dst_buffer, &dst);
6244 }
6245 else
6246 {
6247 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("DDI: unsupported src copy object in DdiMedia_copy.");
6248 }
6249
6250 if (src_obj->obj_type == VACopyObjectSurface)
6251 {
6252 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)src_obj->object.surface_id, mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "copy_src", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
6253 src_surface = DdiMedia_GetSurfaceFromVASurfaceID(mediaCtx, src_obj->object.surface_id);
6254 DDI_CHK_NULL(src_surface, "nullptr surface", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
6255 DDI_CHK_NULL(src_surface->pGmmResourceInfo, "nullptr src_surface->pGmmResourceInfo", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6256
6257 MOS_ZeroMemory(&src, sizeof(src));
6258 DdiMedia_MediaSurfaceToMosResource(src_surface, &src);
6259 }
6260 else if (src_obj->obj_type == VACopyObjectBuffer)
6261 {
6262 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)src_obj->object.buffer_id, mediaCtx->pBufferHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "Invalid copy dst buf_id", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER);
6263 src_buffer = DdiMedia_GetBufferFromVABufferID(mediaCtx, src_obj->object.buffer_id);
6264 DDI_CHK_NULL(src_buffer, "nullptr buffer", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER);
6265 DDI_CHK_NULL(src_buffer->pGmmResourceInfo, "nullptr src_buffer->pGmmResourceInfo", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6266
6267 MOS_ZeroMemory(&src, sizeof(src));
6268 DdiMedia_MediaBufferToMosResource(src_buffer, &src);
6269 }
6270 else
6271 {
6272 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("DDI: unsupported dst copy object in DdiMedia_copy.");
6273 }
6274
6275 mosCtx.bufmgr = mediaCtx->pDrmBufMgr;
6276 mosCtx.m_gpuContextMgr = mediaCtx->m_gpuContextMgr;
6277 mosCtx.m_cmdBufMgr = mediaCtx->m_cmdBufMgr;
6278 mosCtx.fd = mediaCtx->fd;
6279 mosCtx.iDeviceId = mediaCtx->iDeviceId;
6280 mosCtx.m_skuTable = mediaCtx->SkuTable;
6281 mosCtx.m_waTable = mediaCtx->WaTable;
6282 mosCtx.m_gtSystemInfo = *mediaCtx->pGtSystemInfo;
6283 mosCtx.m_platform = mediaCtx->platform;
6284
6285 mosCtx.ppMediaCopyState = &mediaCtx->pMediaCopyState;
6286 mosCtx.m_gtSystemInfo = *mediaCtx->pGtSystemInfo;
6287 mosCtx.m_auxTableMgr = mediaCtx->m_auxTableMgr;
6288 mosCtx.pGmmClientContext = mediaCtx->pGmmClientContext;
6289
6290 mosCtx.m_osDeviceContext = mediaCtx->m_osDeviceContext;
6291 mosCtx.m_apoMosEnabled = mediaCtx->m_apoMosEnabled;
6292 mosCtx.pPerfData = mediaCtx->perfData;
6293 mosCtx.m_userSettingPtr = mediaCtx->m_userSettingPtr;
6294
6295 pCpDdiInterface = Create_DdiCpInterface(mosCtx);
6296
6297 if (nullptr == pCpDdiInterface)
6298 {
6299 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_ALLOCATION_FAILED;
6300 }
6301
6302 vaStatus = DdiMedia_CopyInternal(&mosCtx, &src, &dst, option.bits.va_copy_mode);
6303
6304 if ((option.bits.va_copy_sync == VA_EXEC_SYNC) && dst_surface)
6305 {
6306 uint32_t timeout_NS = 100000000;
6307 while (0 != mos_bo_wait(dst_surface->bo, timeout_NS))
6308 {
6309 // Just loop while gem_bo_wait times-out.
6310 }
6311 }
6312
6313 if (pCpDdiInterface)
6314 {
6315 Delete_DdiCpInterface(pCpDdiInterface);
6316 pCpDdiInterface = NULL;
6317 }
6318
6319 return vaStatus;
6320}
6321#endif

6340VAStatus DdiMedia_BufferInfo (
6341 VADriverContextP ctx,
6342 VABufferID buf_id,
6343 VABufferType *type,
6344 uint32_t *size,
6345 uint32_t *num_elements)
6346{
6347 DDI_FUNCTION_ENTER();
6348
6349 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "nullptr ctx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6350 DDI_CHK_NULL(type, "nullptr type", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6351 DDI_CHK_NULL(size, "nullptr size", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6352 DDI_CHK_NULL(num_elements, "nullptr num_elements", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6353
6354 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
6355 if (nullptr == mediaCtx)
6356 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT;
6357
6358 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->pBufferHeap, "nullptr mediaCtx->pBufferHeap", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6359 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)buf_id, mediaCtx->pBufferHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "Invalid buf_id", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER);
6360
6361 DDI_MEDIA_BUFFER *buf = DdiMedia_GetBufferFromVABufferID(mediaCtx, buf_id);
6362 if (nullptr == buf)
6363 {
6364 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER;
6365 }
6366
6367 *type = (VABufferType)buf->uiType;
6368 *size = buf->iSize / buf->uiNumElements;
6369 *num_elements = buf->uiNumElements;
6370
6371 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
6372}
6373
6403VAStatus DdiMedia_LockSurface (
6404 VADriverContextP ctx,
6405 VASurfaceID surface,
6406 uint32_t *fourcc,
6407 uint32_t *luma_stride,
6408 uint32_t *chroma_u_stride,
6409 uint32_t *chroma_v_stride,
6410 uint32_t *luma_offset,
6411 uint32_t *chroma_u_offset,
6412 uint32_t *chroma_v_offset,
6413 uint32_t *buffer_name,
6414 void **buffer )
6415{
6416 DDI_FUNCTION_ENTER();
6417 MOS_TraceEventExt(EVENT_VA_LOCK, EVENT_TYPE_START, &surface, sizeof(surface), nullptr, 0);
6418
6419 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "nullptr context", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6420 DDI_CHK_NULL(fourcc, "nullptr fourcc", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6421 DDI_CHK_NULL(luma_stride, "nullptr luma_stride", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6422 DDI_CHK_NULL(chroma_u_stride, "nullptr chroma_u_stride", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6423 DDI_CHK_NULL(chroma_v_stride, "nullptr chroma_v_stride", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6424 DDI_CHK_NULL(luma_offset, "nullptr luma_offset", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6425 DDI_CHK_NULL(chroma_u_offset, "nullptr chroma_u_offset", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6426 DDI_CHK_NULL(chroma_v_offset, "nullptr chroma_v_offset", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6427 DDI_CHK_NULL(buffer_name, "nullptr buffer_name", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6428 DDI_CHK_NULL(buffer, "nullptr buffer", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6429
6430 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
6431 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx, "nullptr Media", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6432 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap, "nullptr mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6433 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)surface, mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "Invalid surface", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
6434
6435 DDI_MEDIA_SURFACE *mediaSurface = DdiMedia_GetSurfaceFromVASurfaceID(mediaCtx, surface);
6436
6437#ifdef _MMC_SUPPORTED
6438 // Decompress surface is needed
6439 DdiMedia_MediaMemoryDecompress(mediaCtx, mediaSurface);
6440#endif
6441
6442 if (nullptr == mediaSurface)
6443 {
6444 // Surface is absent.
6445 buffer = nullptr;
6446 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE;
6447 }
6448
6449 if (mediaSurface->uiLockedImageID != VA_INVALID_ID)
6450 {
6451 // Surface is locked already.
6452 buffer = nullptr;
6453 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER;
6454 }
6455
6456 VAImage tmpImage;
6457 tmpImage.image_id = VA_INVALID_ID;
6458 VAStatus vaStatus = DdiMedia_DeriveImage(ctx,surface,&tmpImage);
6459 if (vaStatus != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS)
6460 {
6461 buffer = nullptr;
6462 return vaStatus;
6463 }
6464
6465 mediaSurface->uiLockedImageID = tmpImage.image_id;
6466
6467 vaStatus = DdiMedia_MapBuffer(ctx,tmpImage.buf,buffer);
6468 if (vaStatus != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS)
6469 {
6470 buffer = nullptr;
6471 return vaStatus;
6472 }
6473
6474 mediaSurface->uiLockedBufID = tmpImage.buf;
6475
6476 *fourcc = tmpImage.format.fourcc;
6477 *luma_offset = tmpImage.offsets[0];
6478 *luma_stride = tmpImage.pitches[0];
6479 *chroma_u_offset = tmpImage.offsets[1];
6480 *chroma_u_stride = tmpImage.pitches[1];
6481 *chroma_v_offset = tmpImage.offsets[2];
6482 *chroma_v_stride = tmpImage.pitches[2];
6483 *buffer_name = tmpImage.buf;
6484
6485 MOS_TraceEventExt(EVENT_VA_LOCK, EVENT_TYPE_END, nullptr, 0, nullptr, 0);
6486 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
6487}
6488
6500VAStatus DdiMedia_UnlockSurface (
6501 VADriverContextP ctx,
6502 VASurfaceID surface)
6503{
6504 DDI_FUNCTION_ENTER();
6505 MOS_TraceEventExt(EVENT_VA_UNLOCK, EVENT_TYPE_START, &surface, sizeof(surface), nullptr, 0);
6506
6507 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "nullptr ctx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6508
6509 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
6510 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx, "nullptr mediaCtx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6511 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap, "nullptr mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6512 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)surface, mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "Invalid surface", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
6513
6514 DDI_MEDIA_SURFACE *mediaSurface = DdiMedia_GetSurfaceFromVASurfaceID(mediaCtx, surface);
6515 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaSurface, "nullptr mediaSurface", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
6516
6517 if (mediaSurface->uiLockedImageID == VA_INVALID_ID)
6518 {
6519 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER;
6520 }
6521
6522 VABufferID bufID = (VABufferID)(mediaSurface->uiLockedBufID);
6523 VAStatus vaStatus = DdiMedia_UnmapBuffer(ctx, bufID);
6524 if (vaStatus != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS)
6525 {
6526 return vaStatus;
6527 }
6528 mediaSurface->uiLockedBufID = VA_INVALID_ID;
6529
6530 VAImageID imageID = (VAImageID)(mediaSurface->uiLockedImageID);
6531 vaStatus = DdiMedia_DestroyImage(ctx,imageID);
6532 if (vaStatus != VA_STATUS_SUCCESS)
6533 {
6534 return vaStatus;
6535 }
6536 mediaSurface->uiLockedImageID = VA_INVALID_ID;
6537
6538 MOS_TraceEventExt(EVENT_VA_UNLOCK, EVENT_TYPE_END, nullptr, 0, nullptr, 0);
6539 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
6540}
6541
6557VAStatus
6558DdiMedia_QueryVideoProcFilters(
6559 VADriverContextP ctx,
6560 VAContextID context,
6561 VAProcFilterType *filters,
6562 uint32_t *num_filters)
6563{
6564 DDI_UNUSED(ctx);
6565 DDI_UNUSED(context);
6566
6567 DDI_FUNCTION_ENTER();
6568
6569 DDI_CHK_NULL(filters, "nullptr filters", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6570 DDI_CHK_NULL(num_filters, "nullptr num_filters", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6571
6572 uint32_t max_num_filters = DDI_VP_MAX_NUM_FILTERS;
6573 // check if array size is less than VP_MAX_NUM_FILTERS
6574 if(*num_filters < max_num_filters)
6575 {
6576 DDI_NORMALMESSAGE("num_filters %d < max_num_filters %d. Probably caused by Libva version upgrade!", *num_filters, max_num_filters);
6577 }
6578
6579 // Set the filters
6580 uint32_t i = 0;
6581 uint32_t num_supported_filters = 0;
6582 while(num_supported_filters < *num_filters && i < DDI_VP_MAX_NUM_FILTERS)
6583 {
6584 uint32_t num_filter_caps = 0;
6585 VAStatus vaStatus = DdiVp_QueryVideoProcFilterCaps(ctx, context, vp_supported_filters[i], nullptr, &num_filter_caps);
6586 if(vaStatus == VA_STATUS_SUCCESS && num_filter_caps != 0)
6587 {
6588 filters[num_supported_filters] = vp_supported_filters[i];
6589 num_supported_filters++;
6590 }
6591 i++;
6592 }
6593
6594 // Tell the app how many valid filters are filled in the array
6595 *num_filters = num_supported_filters;
6596
6597 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
6598}

6619DdiMedia_QueryVideoProcFilterCaps(

6625)

6629 return DdiVp_QueryVideoProcFilterCaps(ctx, context, type, filter_caps, num_filter_caps);
6630}

6649VAStatus
6650DdiMedia_QueryVideoProcPipelineCaps(
6651 VADriverContextP ctx,
6652 VAContextID context,
6653 VABufferID *filters,
6654 uint32_t num_filters,
6655 VAProcPipelineCaps *pipeline_caps
6656)
6657{
6658 DDI_FUNCTION_ENTER();
6659
6660 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
6661
6662 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "nullptr ctx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6663 DDI_CHK_NULL(pipeline_caps, "nullptr pipeline_caps", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6664 if (num_filters > 0)
6665 DDI_CHK_NULL(filters, "nullptr filters", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6666
6667 pipeline_caps->pipeline_flags = VA_PROC_PIPELINE_FAST;
6668 pipeline_caps->filter_flags = 0;
6669 pipeline_caps->rotation_flags = (1 << VA_ROTATION_NONE) | (1 << VA_ROTATION_90) | (1 << VA_ROTATION_180) | (1 << VA_ROTATION_270);
6670 pipeline_caps->mirror_flags = VA_MIRROR_HORIZONTAL | VA_MIRROR_VERTICAL;
6671 pipeline_caps->blend_flags = VA_BLEND_GLOBAL_ALPHA | VA_BLEND_PREMULTIPLIED_ALPHA | VA_BLEND_LUMA_KEY;
6672 pipeline_caps->num_forward_references = DDI_CODEC_NUM_FWD_REF;
6673 pipeline_caps->num_backward_references = DDI_CODEC_NUM_BK_REF;
6674 pipeline_caps->input_color_standards = vp_input_color_std;
6675 pipeline_caps->num_input_color_standards = DDI_VP_NUM_INPUT_COLOR_STD;
6676 pipeline_caps->output_color_standards = vp_output_color_std;
6677 pipeline_caps->num_output_color_standards = DDI_VP_NUM_OUT_COLOR_STD;
6678
6679 if ((context & DDI_MEDIA_MASK_VACONTEXT_TYPE) == DDI_MEDIA_VACONTEXTID_OFFSET_DECODER)
6680 {
6681 //Decode+SFC, go SFC path, the restriction here is the capability of SFC
6682 pipeline_caps->num_input_pixel_formats = 1;
6683 pipeline_caps->input_pixel_format[0] = VA_FOURCC_NV12;
6684 pipeline_caps->num_output_pixel_formats = 1;
6685 pipeline_caps->output_pixel_format[0] = VA_FOURCC_NV12;
6686 if((MEDIA_IS_SKU(&(mediaCtx->SkuTable), FtrHCP2SFCPipe)))
6687 {
6688 pipeline_caps->max_input_width = DDI_DECODE_HCP_SFC_MAX_WIDTH;
6689 pipeline_caps->max_input_height = DDI_DECODE_HCP_SFC_MAX_HEIGHT;
6690 }
6691 else
6692 {
6693 pipeline_caps->max_input_width = DDI_DECODE_SFC_MAX_WIDTH;
6694 pipeline_caps->max_input_height = DDI_DECODE_SFC_MAX_HEIGHT;
6695 }
6696 pipeline_caps->min_input_width = DDI_DECODE_SFC_MIN_WIDTH;
6697 pipeline_caps->min_input_height = DDI_DECODE_SFC_MIN_HEIGHT;
6698 pipeline_caps->max_output_width = DDI_DECODE_SFC_MAX_WIDTH;
6699 pipeline_caps->max_output_height = DDI_DECODE_SFC_MAX_HEIGHT;
6700 pipeline_caps->min_output_width = DDI_DECODE_SFC_MIN_WIDTH;
6701 pipeline_caps->min_output_height = DDI_DECODE_SFC_MIN_HEIGHT;
6702 }
6703 else if ((context & DDI_MEDIA_MASK_VACONTEXT_TYPE) == DDI_MEDIA_VACONTEXTID_OFFSET_VP)
6704 {
6705 if(mediaCtx->platform.eRenderCoreFamily <= IGFX_GEN8_CORE)
6706 {
6707 //Capability of Gen8- platform
6708 pipeline_caps->max_input_width = VP_MAX_PIC_WIDTH_Gen8;
6709 pipeline_caps->max_input_height = VP_MAX_PIC_HEIGHT_Gen8;
6710 pipeline_caps->max_output_width = VP_MAX_PIC_WIDTH_Gen8;
6711 pipeline_caps->max_output_height = VP_MAX_PIC_HEIGHT_Gen8;
6712 }else
6713 {
6714 //Capability of Gen9+ platform
6715 pipeline_caps->max_input_width = VP_MAX_PIC_WIDTH;
6716 pipeline_caps->max_input_height = VP_MAX_PIC_HEIGHT;
6717 pipeline_caps->max_output_width = VP_MAX_PIC_WIDTH;
6718 pipeline_caps->max_output_height = VP_MAX_PIC_HEIGHT;
6719 }
6720 pipeline_caps->min_input_width = VP_MIN_PIC_WIDTH;
6721 pipeline_caps->min_input_height = VP_MIN_PIC_HEIGHT;
6722 pipeline_caps->min_output_width = VP_MIN_PIC_WIDTH;
6723 pipeline_caps->min_output_height = VP_MIN_PIC_WIDTH;
6724 }
6725 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
6726}

6764}
6765
6779VAStatus DdiMedia_AcquireBufferHandle(
6780 VADriverContextP ctx,
6781 VABufferID buf_id,
6782 VABufferInfo *buf_info)
6783{
6784 DDI_FUNCTION_ENTER();
6785
6786 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "nullptr ctx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6787 DDI_CHK_NULL(buf_info, "nullptr buf_info", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6788
6789 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
6790 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx, "Invalid Media ctx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6791
6792 DDI_MEDIA_BUFFER *buf = DdiMedia_GetBufferFromVABufferID(mediaCtx, buf_id);
6793 DDI_CHK_NULL(buf, "Invalid Media Buffer", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER);
6794 DDI_CHK_NULL(buf->bo, "Invalid Media Buffer", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER);
6795
6796 // If user did not specify memtype he want's we use something we prefer, we prefer PRIME
6797 if (!buf_info->mem_type)
6798 {
6799 buf_info->mem_type = VA_SURFACE_ATTRIB_MEM_TYPE_DRM_PRIME;
6800 }
6801 // now chekcing memtype whether we support it
6802 if ((buf_info->mem_type != VA_SURFACE_ATTRIB_MEM_TYPE_DRM_PRIME) &&
6803 (buf_info->mem_type != VA_SURFACE_ATTRIB_MEM_TYPE_KERNEL_DRM))
6804 {
6805 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_UNSUPPORTED_MEMORY_TYPE;
6806 }
6807
6808 DdiMediaUtil_LockMutex(&mediaCtx->BufferMutex);
6809 // already acquired?
6810 if (buf->uiExportcount)
6811 { // yes, already acquired
6812 // can't provide access thru another memtype
6813 if (buf->uiMemtype != buf_info->mem_type)
6814 {
6815 DdiMediaUtil_UnLockMutex(&mediaCtx->BufferMutex);
6816 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER;
6817 }
6818 }
6819 else
6820 { // no, not acquired - doing this now
6821 switch (buf_info->mem_type) {
6822 case VA_SURFACE_ATTRIB_MEM_TYPE_KERNEL_DRM: {
6823 uint32_t flink = 0;
6824 if (mos_bo_flink(buf->bo, &flink) != 0)
6825 {
6826 DdiMediaUtil_UnLockMutex(&mediaCtx->BufferMutex);
6827 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER;
6828 }
6829 buf->handle = (intptr_t)flink;
6830 break;
6831 }
6832 case VA_SURFACE_ATTRIB_MEM_TYPE_DRM_PRIME: {
6833 int32_t prime_fd = 0;
6834 if (mos_bo_export_to_prime(buf->bo, &prime_fd) != 0)
6835 {
6836 DdiMediaUtil_UnLockMutex(&mediaCtx->BufferMutex);
6837 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER;
6838 }
6839
6840 buf->handle = (intptr_t)prime_fd;
6841 break;
6842 }
6843 }
6844 // saving memtepy which was provided to the user
6845 buf->uiMemtype = buf_info->mem_type;
6846 }
6847
6848 ++buf->uiExportcount;
6849 mos_bo_reference(buf->bo);
6850
6851 buf_info->type = buf->uiType;
6852 buf_info->handle = buf->handle;
6853 buf_info->mem_size = buf->uiNumElements * buf->iSize;
6854
6855 DdiMediaUtil_UnLockMutex(&mediaCtx->BufferMutex);
6856 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
6857}
6858
6870VAStatus DdiMedia_ReleaseBufferHandle(
6871 VADriverContextP ctx,
6872 VABufferID buf_id)
6873{
6874 DDI_FUNCTION_ENTER();
6875
6876 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "nullptr ctx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6877
6878 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
6879 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx, "Invalid Media ctx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
6880
6881 DDI_MEDIA_BUFFER *buf = DdiMedia_GetBufferFromVABufferID(mediaCtx, buf_id);
6882 DDI_CHK_NULL(buf, "Invalid Media Buffer", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER);
6883 DDI_CHK_NULL(buf->bo, "Invalid Media Buffer", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_BUFFER);
6884
6885 DdiMediaUtil_LockMutex(&mediaCtx->BufferMutex);
6886 if (!buf->uiMemtype || !buf->uiExportcount)
6887 {
6888 DdiMediaUtil_UnLockMutex(&mediaCtx->BufferMutex);
6889 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
6890 }
6891 mos_bo_unreference(buf->bo);
6892 --buf->uiExportcount;
6893
6894 if (!buf->uiExportcount) {
6895 switch (buf->uiMemtype) {
6896 case VA_SURFACE_ATTRIB_MEM_TYPE_DRM_PRIME: {
6897 close((intptr_t)buf->handle);
6898 break;
6899 }
6900 }
6901 buf->uiMemtype = 0;
6902 }
6903 DdiMediaUtil_UnLockMutex(&mediaCtx->BufferMutex);
6904
6905 if (!buf->uiExportcount && buf->bPostponedBufFree) {
6906 MOS_FreeMemory(buf);
6907 DdiMedia_DestroyBufFromVABufferID(mediaCtx, buf_id);
6908 }
6909
6910 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
6911}
6912
6913static uint32_t DdiMedia_GetPlaneNum(PDDI_MEDIA_SURFACE mediaSurface, bool hasAuxPlane)
6914{
6915 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaSurface, "nullptr mediaSurface", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
6916
6917 uint32_t fourcc = DdiMedia_MediaFormatToOsFormat(mediaSurface->format);
6918 uint32_t plane_num = 0;
6919 switch(fourcc)
6920 {
6921 case VA_FOURCC_NV12:
6922 case VA_FOURCC_NV21:
6923 case VA_FOURCC_P010:
6924 case VA_FOURCC_P012:
6925 case VA_FOURCC_P016:
6926 plane_num = hasAuxPlane ? 4 : 2;
6927 break;
6928 case VA_FOURCC_I420:
6929 case VA_FOURCC_YV12:
6930 case VA_FOURCC_411P:
6931 case VA_FOURCC_422H:
6932 case VA_FOURCC_422V:
6933 case VA_FOURCC_444P:
6934 case VA_FOURCC_IMC3:
6935 case VA_FOURCC_RGBP:
6936 case VA_FOURCC_BGRP:
6937 plane_num = 3;
6938 break;
6939 case VA_FOURCC_YUY2:
6940 case VA_FOURCC_UYVY:
6941 case VA_FOURCC_YVYU:
6942 case VA_FOURCC_VYUY:
6943 case VA_FOURCC_Y800:
6944 case VA_FOURCC_Y210:
6945#if VA_CHECK_VERSION(1, 9, 0)
6946 case VA_FOURCC_Y212:
6947#endif
6948 case VA_FOURCC_Y216:
6949 case VA_FOURCC_Y410:
6950#if VA_CHECK_VERSION(1, 9, 0)
6951 case VA_FOURCC_Y412:
6952#endif
6953 case VA_FOURCC_Y416:
6954 case VA_FOURCC_AYUV:
6955#if VA_CHECK_VERSION(1, 13, 0)
6956 case VA_FOURCC_XYUV:
6957#endif
6958 case VA_FOURCC_RGBA:
6959 case VA_FOURCC_RGBX:
6960 case VA_FOURCC_BGRA:
6961 case VA_FOURCC_BGRX:
6962 case VA_FOURCC_ARGB:
6963 case VA_FOURCC_ABGR:
6964 case VA_FOURCC_XRGB:
6965 case VA_FOURCC_XBGR:
6966 case VA_FOURCC_RGB565:
6967 case VA_FOURCC_R8G8B8:
6968 case VA_FOURCC_A2R10G10B10:
6969 case VA_FOURCC_A2B10G10R10:
6970 case VA_FOURCC_X2R10G10B10:
6971 case VA_FOURCC_X2B10G10R10:
6972 plane_num = hasAuxPlane ? 2 : 1;
6973 break;
6974 default:
6975 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("Unsupported format.\n");
6976 }
6977 return plane_num;
6978}
6979

6981{
6982 if (plane == 0)
6983 {

6985 {
6986 case VA_FOURCC_NV12:
6987 case VA_FOURCC_I420:

6992 case VA_FOURCC_422V:

7000 case VA_FOURCC_P016:

7003

7010 case VA_FOURCC_UYVY:
7011 return DRM_FORMAT_UYVY;

7013 return DRM_FORMAT_AYUV;
7014#if VA_CHECK_VERSION(1, 13, 0)
7015 case VA_FOURCC_XYUV:
7016 return DRM_FORMAT_XYUV8888;
7017#endif
7018 case VA_FOURCC_Y210:
7019 return DRM_FORMAT_Y210;
7020 case VA_FOURCC_Y216:
7021 return DRM_FORMAT_Y216;
7022 case VA_FOURCC_Y410:
7023 return DRM_FORMAT_Y410;
7024 case VA_FOURCC_Y416:
7025 return DRM_FORMAT_Y416;
7026#if VA_CHECK_VERSION(1, 9, 0)
7027 case VA_FOURCC_Y212:
7028 return DRM_FORMAT_Y216;
7029 case VA_FOURCC_Y412:
7030 return DRM_FORMAT_Y416;
7031#endif
7032
7033 case VA_FOURCC_ARGB:
7034 return DRM_FORMAT_ARGB8888;
7035 case VA_FOURCC_ABGR:
7036 return DRM_FORMAT_ABGR8888;
7037 case VA_FOURCC_RGBA:
7038 return DRM_FORMAT_RGBA8888;
7039 case VA_FOURCC_BGRA:
7040 return DRM_FORMAT_BGRA8888;
7041 case VA_FOURCC_XRGB:
7042 return DRM_FORMAT_XRGB8888;
7043 case VA_FOURCC_XBGR:
7044 return DRM_FORMAT_XBGR8888;
7045 case VA_FOURCC_RGBX:
7046 return DRM_FORMAT_RGBX8888;
7047 case VA_FOURCC_BGRX:
7048 return DRM_FORMAT_BGRX8888;
7049 case VA_FOURCC_A2R10G10B10:
7050 return DRM_FORMAT_ARGB2101010;
7051 case VA_FOURCC_A2B10G10R10:
7052 return DRM_FORMAT_ABGR2101010;
7053 case VA_FOURCC_X2R10G10B10:
7054 return DRM_FORMAT_XRGB2101010;
7055 case VA_FOURCC_X2B10G10R10:
7056 return DRM_FORMAT_XBGR2101010;
7057 }
7058 }
7059 else
7060 {
7061 switch (fourcc)
7062 {
7063 case VA_FOURCC_NV12:
7064 return DRM_FORMAT_GR88;
7065 case VA_FOURCC_I420:
7066 case VA_FOURCC_IMC3:
7067 case VA_FOURCC_YV12:
7068 case VA_FOURCC_YV16:
7069 case VA_FOURCC_422H:
7070 case VA_FOURCC_422V:
7071 case VA_FOURCC_444P:
7072 case VA_FOURCC_RGBP:
7073 case VA_FOURCC_BGRP:
7074 return DRM_FORMAT_R8;
7075 case VA_FOURCC_P010:
7076 case VA_FOURCC_P012:
7077 case VA_FOURCC_P016:
7078 return DRM_FORMAT_GR1616;
7079 case VA_FOURCC_I010:
7080 return DRM_FORMAT_R16;
7081 }
7082 }
7083 return 0;
7084}

7170
7171
7190VAStatus DdiMedia_ExportSurfaceHandle(
7191 VADriverContextP ctx,
7192 VASurfaceID surface_id,
7193 uint32_t mem_type,
7194 uint32_t flags,
7195 void * descriptor)
7196{
7197 DDI_CHK_NULL(descriptor, "nullptr descriptor", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
7198 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "nullptr ctx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
7199
7200 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
7201 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx, "nullptr mediaCtx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
7202 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap, "nullptr mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
7203 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)(surface_id), mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "Invalid surfaces", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
7204
7205 DDI_MEDIA_SURFACE *mediaSurface = DdiMedia_GetSurfaceFromVASurfaceID(mediaCtx, surface_id);
7206 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaSurface, "nullptr mediaSurface", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
7207 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaSurface->bo, "nullptr mediaSurface->bo", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
7208 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaSurface->pGmmResourceInfo, "nullptr mediaSurface->pGmmResourceInfo", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
7209
7210 if (
7211#if VA_CHECK_VERSION(1, 21, 0)
7212 mem_type != VA_SURFACE_ATTRIB_MEM_TYPE_DRM_PRIME_3 &&
7213#endif
7214 mem_type != VA_SURFACE_ATTRIB_MEM_TYPE_DRM_PRIME_2)
7215 {
7216 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("vaExportSurfaceHandle: memory type %08x is not supported.\n", mem_type);
7217 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_UNSUPPORTED_MEMORY_TYPE;
7218 }
7219
7220 if (mos_bo_export_to_prime(mediaSurface->bo, (int32_t*)&mediaSurface->name))
7221 {
7222 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("Failed drm_intel_gem_export_to_prime operation!!!\n");
7223 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_OPERATION_FAILED;
7224 }
7225
7226 VADRMPRIMESurfaceDescriptor *desc = (VADRMPRIMESurfaceDescriptor *)descriptor;
7227
7228#if VA_CHECK_VERSION(1, 21, 0)
7229 if(mem_type == VA_SURFACE_ATTRIB_MEM_TYPE_DRM_PRIME_3)
7230 {
7231 VADRMPRIME3SurfaceDescriptor *desc = (VADRMPRIME3SurfaceDescriptor *)descriptor;
7232 if(mediaSurface->pGmmResourceInfo->GetSetCpSurfTag(false, 0))
7233 {
7234 desc->flags |= VA_SURFACE_EXTBUF_DESC_PROTECTED;
7235 }
7236 }
7237#endif
7238
7239 desc->fourcc = DdiMedia_MediaFormatToOsFormat(mediaSurface->format);
7240 if(desc->fourcc == VA_STATUS_ERROR_UNSUPPORTED_RT_FORMAT)
7241 {
7242 // close the handle to avoid leak
7243 close(mediaSurface->name);
7244 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_UNSUPPORTED_RT_FORMAT;
7245 }
7246 desc->width = mediaSurface->iWidth;
7247 desc->height = mediaSurface->iRealHeight;
7248 desc->num_objects = 1;
7249 desc->objects[0].fd = mediaSurface->name;
7250 desc->objects[0].size = mediaSurface->pGmmResourceInfo->GetSizeSurface();
7251
7252 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->m_caps, "nullptr m_caps", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
7253
7254 if(VA_STATUS_SUCCESS != mediaCtx->m_caps->GetSurfaceModifier(mediaSurface, desc->objects[0].drm_format_modifier))
7255 {
7256 close(mediaSurface->name);
7257 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("could not find related modifier values");
7258 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_UNSUPPORTED_RT_FORMAT;
7259 }
7260
7261 int composite_object = flags & VA_EXPORT_SURFACE_COMPOSED_LAYERS;
7262
7263 uint32_t formats[4];
7264
7265 // Query Aux Plane info form GMM
7266 bool hasAuxPlane = false;
7267 GMM_RESOURCE_FLAG GmmFlags = mediaSurface->pGmmResourceInfo->GetResFlags();
7268
7269 if (((GmmFlags.Gpu.MMC ||
7270 GmmFlags.Gpu.CCS) &&
7271 (GmmFlags.Info.MediaCompressed ||
7272 GmmFlags.Info.RenderCompressed) &&
7273 mediaCtx->m_auxTableMgr) )
7274 {
7275 hasAuxPlane = true;
7276 }
7277 else
7278 {
7279 hasAuxPlane = false;
7280 }
7281
7282 uint32_t num_planes = DdiMedia_GetPlaneNum(mediaSurface, hasAuxPlane);
7283
7284 if(composite_object)
7285 {
7286 formats[0] = DdiMedia_GetDrmFormatOfCompositeObject(desc->fourcc);
7287 if(!formats[0])
7288 {
7289 close(mediaSurface->name);
7290 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("vaExportSurfaceHandle: fourcc %08x is not supported for export as a composite object.\n", desc->fourcc);
7291 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE;
7292 }
7293 }
7294 else
7295 {
7296 for (int i = 0; i < num_planes; i++)
7297 {
7298 formats[i] = DdiMedia_GetDrmFormatOfSeparatePlane(desc->fourcc,i);
7299 if (!formats[i])
7300 {
7301 close(mediaSurface->name);
7302 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("vaExportSurfaceHandle: fourcc %08x is not supported for export as separate planes.\n", desc->fourcc);
7303 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE;
7304 }
7305 }
7306 }
7307
7308 uint32_t pitch, height, chromaPitch, chromaHeight = 0;
7309 pitch = mediaSurface->iPitch;
7310 height = mediaSurface->iRealHeight;
7311 DdiMedia_GetChromaPitchHeight(desc->fourcc, pitch, height, &chromaPitch, &chromaHeight);
7312
7313 // Get Yoffset from GMM
7314 GMM_REQ_OFFSET_INFO reqInfo = {0};
7315 reqInfo.Plane = GMM_PLANE_Y;
7316 reqInfo.ReqRender = 1;
7317 mediaSurface->pGmmResourceInfo->GetOffset(reqInfo);
7318 uint32_t offsetY = reqInfo.Render.Offset;
7319
7320 // Get Uoffset from GMM
7321 MOS_ZeroMemory(&reqInfo, sizeof(GMM_REQ_OFFSET_INFO));
7322 reqInfo.Plane = GMM_PLANE_U;
7323 reqInfo.ReqRender = 1;
7324 mediaSurface->pGmmResourceInfo->GetOffset(reqInfo);
7325 uint32_t offsetU = reqInfo.Render.Offset;
7326
7327 // Get Voffset from GMM
7328 MOS_ZeroMemory(&reqInfo, sizeof(GMM_REQ_OFFSET_INFO));
7329 reqInfo.Plane = GMM_PLANE_V;
7330 reqInfo.ReqRender = 1;
7331 mediaSurface->pGmmResourceInfo->GetOffset(reqInfo);
7332 uint32_t offsetV = reqInfo.Render.Offset;
7333
7334 // Get Aux Plane offset
7335 uint32_t auxOffsetY = (uint32_t)mediaSurface->pGmmResourceInfo->GetPlanarAuxOffset(0, GMM_AUX_Y_CCS);
7336 uint32_t auxOffsetUV = (uint32_t)mediaSurface->pGmmResourceInfo->GetPlanarAuxOffset(0, GMM_AUX_UV_CCS);
7337
7338 if (composite_object) {
7339 desc->num_layers = 1;
7340 desc->layers[0].drm_format = formats[0];
7341 desc->layers[0].num_planes = num_planes;
7342 if (hasAuxPlane)
7343 {
7344 // For semi-planar formats like NV12, CCS planes follow the Y and UV planes,
7345 // i.e. planes 0 and 1 are used for Y and UV surfaces, planes 2 and 3 for the respective CCS.
7346 for (int i = 0; i < num_planes/2; i++)
7347 {
7348 desc->layers[0].object_index[2*i] = 0;
7349 desc->layers[0].object_index[2*i+1] = 0;
7350 if (i == 0)
7351 {
7352 // Y plane
7353 desc->layers[0].offset[i] = offsetY;
7354 desc->layers[0].pitch[i] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
7355 // Y aux plane
7356 desc->layers[0].offset[i + num_planes/2] = auxOffsetY;
7357 desc->layers[0].pitch[i + num_planes/2] = mediaSurface->iPitch/8;
7358 }
7359 else
7360 {
7361 // UV plane
7362 desc->layers[0].offset[i] = offsetU;
7363 desc->layers[0].pitch[i] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
7364 // UV aux plane
7365 desc->layers[0].offset[i + num_planes/2] = auxOffsetUV;
7366 desc->layers[0].pitch[i + num_planes/2] = mediaSurface->iPitch/8;
7367 }
7368 }
7369 }else
7370 {
7371 for (int i = 0; i < num_planes; i++)
7372 {
7373 desc->layers[0].object_index[i] = 0;
7374 switch(i)
7375 {
7376 case 0:
7377 desc->layers[0].offset[i] = offsetY;
7378 desc->layers[0].pitch[i] = pitch;
7379 break;
7380 case 1:
7381 if (desc->fourcc == VA_FOURCC_YV12)
7382 {
7383 desc->layers[0].offset[i] = offsetV;
7384 }
7385 else
7386 {
7387 desc->layers[0].offset[i] = offsetU;
7388 }
7389 desc->layers[0].pitch[i] = chromaPitch;
7390 break;
7391 case 2:
7392 if (desc->fourcc == VA_FOURCC_YV12)
7393 {
7394 desc->layers[0].offset[i] = offsetU;
7395 }
7396 else
7397 {
7398 desc->layers[0].offset[i] = offsetV;
7399 }
7400 desc->layers[0].pitch[i] = chromaPitch;
7401 break;
7402 default:
7403 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("vaExportSurfaceHandle: invalid plan numbers");
7404 }
7405 }
7406 }
7407 }
7408 else
7409 {
7410 if (hasAuxPlane)
7411 {
7412 desc->num_layers = num_planes / 2;
7413
7414 for (int i = 0; i < desc->num_layers; i++)
7415 {
7416 desc->layers[i].drm_format = formats[i];
7417 desc->layers[i].num_planes = 2;
7418
7419 desc->layers[i].object_index[0] = 0;
7420
7421 if (i == 0)
7422 {
7423 desc->layers[i].offset[0] = offsetY;
7424 desc->layers[i].offset[1] = auxOffsetY;
7425 desc->layers[i].pitch[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
7426 desc->layers[i].pitch[1] = mediaSurface->iPitch/8;
7427 }
7428 else
7429 {
7430 desc->layers[i].offset[0] = offsetU;
7431 desc->layers[i].offset[1] = auxOffsetUV;
7432 desc->layers[i].pitch[0] = mediaSurface->iPitch;
7433 desc->layers[i].pitch[1] = mediaSurface->iPitch/8;
7434 }
7435 }
7436 }else
7437 {
7438 desc->num_layers = num_planes;
7439
7440 for (int i = 0; i < num_planes; i++)
7441 {
7442 desc->layers[i].drm_format = formats[i];
7443 desc->layers[i].num_planes = 1;
7444
7445 desc->layers[i].object_index[0] = 0;
7446
7447 switch(i)
7448 {
7449 case 0:
7450 desc->layers[i].offset[0] = offsetY;
7451 desc->layers[i].pitch[0] = pitch;
7452 break;
7453 case 1:
7454 if (desc->fourcc == VA_FOURCC_YV12)
7455 {
7456 desc->layers[i].offset[0] = offsetV;
7457 }
7458 else
7459 {
7460 desc->layers[i].offset[0] = offsetU;
7461 }
7462 desc->layers[i].pitch[0] = chromaPitch;
7463 break;
7464 case 2:
7465 if (desc->fourcc == VA_FOURCC_YV12)
7466 {
7467 desc->layers[i].offset[0] = offsetU;
7468 }
7469 else
7470 {
7471 desc->layers[i].offset[0] = offsetV;
7472 }
7473 desc->layers[i].pitch[0] = chromaPitch;
7474 break;
7475 default:
7476 DDI_ASSERTMESSAGE("vaExportSurfaceHandle: invalid plan numbers");
7477 }
7478 }
7479 }
7480 }
7481
7482 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
7483}

7497}

7538MEDIAAPI_EXPORT VAStatus DdiMedia_ExtGetSurfaceHandle(
7539 VADisplay dpy,
7540 VASurfaceID *surface,
7541 int32_t *prime_fd)
7542{
7543 DDI_CHK_NULL(dpy, "nullptr dpy", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_DISPLAY);
7544 DDI_CHK_NULL(surface, "nullptr surfaces", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
7545 DDI_CHK_NULL(prime_fd, "nullptr id", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER);
7546
7547 VADriverContextP ctx = ((VADisplayContextP)dpy)->pDriverContext;
7548 DDI_CHK_NULL(ctx, "nullptr ctx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
7549
7550 PDDI_MEDIA_CONTEXT mediaCtx = DdiMedia_GetMediaContext(ctx);
7551 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx, "nullptr mediaCtx", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
7552 DDI_CHK_NULL(mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap, "nullptr mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
7553 DDI_CHK_LESS((uint32_t)(*surface), mediaCtx->pSurfaceHeap->uiAllocatedHeapElements, "Invalid surfaces", VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE);
7554
7555 DDI_MEDIA_SURFACE *mediaSurface = DdiMedia_GetSurfaceFromVASurfaceID(mediaCtx, *surface);
7556 if (mediaSurface)
7557 {
7558 if (mediaSurface->bo)
7559 {
7560 int32_t ret = mos_bo_export_to_prime(mediaSurface->bo, (int32_t*)&mediaSurface->name);
7561 if (ret)
7562 {
7563 //LOGE("Failed drm_intel_gem_export_to_prime operation!!!\n");
7564 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_OPERATION_FAILED;
7565 }
7566 }
7567 }
7568 else
7569 {
7570 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_SURFACE;
7571 }
7572
7573 *prime_fd = mediaSurface->name;
7574
7575 return VA_STATUS_SUCCESS;
7576}

7605 return VA_STATUS_ERROR_INVALID_PARAMETER;

7608}
